自理</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">。</span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">   <o:p></o:p></span></p> <p><font face=\"宋体\"></font></p> <p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.35pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: 2.0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\" lang=\"EN-US\">4.</span><span style=\"color: black; font-size: 7pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体;\">职教师资班：文史类专业（不含外语类）<span lang=\"EN-US\">6000</span>元<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>生·学年，理科类、外语类专业<span lang=\"EN-US\">7000</span>元<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>生·学年，工科类专业<span lang=\"EN-US\">7500</span>元<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>生·学年。<span lang=\"EN-US\">    <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p><font face=\"宋体\"></font></p> <p style=\"background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 31.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">第二十九条</span></b><span style=\"color: black; font-size: 7pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Rom